<h1>About This Project</h1>

<p>
  This is a **Rails Intro Project** where we fetch and display data from **Faker** and the **SWAPI API**.
  The goal is to implement key Rails features such as **ActiveRecord models, relationships, pagination, search, and filtering**.
</p>

<h2>Data Sources</h2>
<ul>
  <li>💾 <strong>Faker</strong>: Used for generating fake Star Wars characters.</li>
  <li>🌐 <strong>SWAPI API</strong>: Fetches real Star Wars characters and films.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Project Features</h2>
<ul>
  <li>✅ <strong>Characters and Films</strong> with full CRUD functionality.</li>
  <li>✅ <strong>Pagination</strong> to handle large data sets efficiently.</li>
  <li>✅ <strong>Search and Filtering</strong> for easy data lookup.</li>
  <li>✅ <strong>Custom Styling</strong> for a clean UI.</li>
</ul>

